        public FailLoadingEvent(Browser browser,
                        long frameId,
                        boolean mainFrame,
                        java.lang.String validatedURL,
                        NetError errorCode,
                        java.lang.String errorDescription)
        Constructs a new FailLoadingEvent instance.
        构造一个新的FailLoadingEvent实例。
        Parameters:
        browser - the browser instance on which the event is initially occurred. -最初发生事件的浏览器实例。
        frameId - identifier of a frame that is failed to download. -下载失败的框架的标识符。
        mainFrame - indicates whether the frameId is a main frame. -指示是否为主机。
        validatedURL - address of a frame which is failed to download. -下载失败的框架地址。
        errorCode - describes the reason of failure. Use NetError to compare. -描述失败的原因。用于比较。
        errorDescription - description of the reason of failure. -故障原因的描述。
